positions.position:
Our Attorney General is the first line of defense against the federal government. As Attorney General,I will: 
1) Work with the Governor to deploy more National Guard troops to the Texas/Mexico border;
2) Toughen criminal penalties on drug smugglers and human traffickers;
3) Finish President Trump’s wall and continue building the Texas wall

1) fight climate change, the most pressing social justice issue of our age, as the harm falls hardest on poor communities; 
2) create more affordable housing; the county is already creating more than 11,000 units, either built or underway; 
3) continue criminal-justice reform, e.g., the first Public Defender Office and the first Sobering Center as an alternative to jail; I helped pass both.
